Output "/output/test.gif"

Set Theme "Dracula"
Set FontSize 12
Set Width 1200
Set Height 700
Set Padding 10
Set TypingSpeed 40ms
Set PlaybackSpeed 0.5
Set Framerate 24

Type "# axios-rat-scan -- scanning 100 npm projects for the axios supply chain RAT"
Enter
Sleep 1s
Type "axios-rat-scan --no-process /projects"
Enter
Sleep 12s
